function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	local followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	local followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_Magic")
	
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_SeeCoffin, followerNeyrelle)
	
	-- Lorath move / talk actions
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerLorath)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerLorath, false)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(followerLorath)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerLorath, idLorathShore, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerLorath, idLorathShore)
	
	-- Neyrelle move actions
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(followerNeyrelle)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerNeyrelle, idNeyrelleShore, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, idNeyrelleShore)
	
	-- Wait for both to be done
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(followerLorath, 0.5)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(followerNeyrelle, 0.5)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idLorath)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idNeyrelle)
	Hydra.ActorSetSheathPreference(idLorath, 1)
	Hydra.ActorSetSheathPreference(idNeyrelle, 1)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idNeyrelle)
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.EventSend("Find Wreckage")
	
end
